title.romaji: HUGtto! Precure ♡ Futari wa Precure All Stars Memories

description:
Celebrating the 15th anniversary of the Precure franchise, and the eleventh Precure All Stars crossover film.

A mysterious monster named Miden has appeared, stealing away the Precures' memories and reverting them to the state of a small child. The HUGtto! Precure team joins forces with the Futari wa Precure team to retrieve the stolen memories and powers of every other Precure team so far!
synonyms: Hugtto! Pretty Cure x Futari wa Pretty Cure Movie: All Stars Memories

node.description:
[Twitter](https://twitter.com/i/user/71842765)

After working for Square Enix and Production I.G, he joined Toei Animation in 2010. He is challenging himself to create works that transcend genres, from realistic to cel-style.

[Wiki (jp)](https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/東堂いづみ) | [Wiki (en)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Izumi_Todo)

Izumi Toudou is a collective pseudonym for [Toei Animation](https://anilist.co/studio/18/)'s staff.

[Twitter](https://twitter.com/i/user/1319638475969183744)

Director and storyboard artist affiliated with [Toei Animation](https://anilist.co/studio/18/Toei-Animation).
Yasuhiro Katou is a CG director.

__Alma Mater:__ Toyo University

__[Website](https://www.yukihayashi.net/)__ | __[Twitter](https://twitter.com/hayayu1231)__

__Introduction:__
Yuuki Hayashi is a Japanese composer and arranger affiliated with Legendoor, who used to be a rhythmic gymnast

__Biography:__
His history in music began in university when he started creating music pieces for rhythmic gymnasts as a hobby for 5000 yen a piece. When he started getting requests from other universities for his music, his interest in music producing grew. After graduation, he was taught music for 6 months by a rhythmic gymnastics music producer, and now, he handles music for various sports. He also arranges music for dance, athletic competitions, companies, independent movies and recently, TV dramas and anime.

(Source: MyAnimeList, edited)
